item.title: CVE-2024-31451|2024-04-19T16:16:04.273Z -- arc53 -- DocsGPT
item.description: DocsGPT is a GPT-powered chat for documentation. DocsGPT is vulnerable to unauthenticated limited file write in routes.py. This vulnerability is fixed in 0.8.1.
